<br>

Magic Potions are an item that {% worker_link alchemist %} craft using [Mistletoe](../../source/items/mistletoe) after completing the {% include links/research.html tree="Combat" name="Panoramix" %} research. Druids will request Magic Potions to increase the strength and duration of their potions.
